usic-features/new-anticipated-album-releases-2025-3826243">NME 2025 年最受期待的专辑发行</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brits">全英音乐</a>奖提名的说唱歌手也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/central-cee-announces-last-minute-london-show-at-koko-3829295">将于 1 月 30 日接手伦敦的 KOKO</a> ，也就是他备受期待的首张专辑《Can&#39;t Rush Greatness》发行六天后。演出门票将于本周五（1 月 17 日）下午 3 点开始发售。请访问<a href="https://koko.seetickets.com/event/central-cee/koko/3283486?pre=spotify&amp;aff=id1linkfire&amp;src=dc7726c70b965037c8315025b9c11b0c" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。</p><p> 《Can&#39;t Rush Greatness》被<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/new-anticipated-album-releases-2025-3826243"><em>NME</em>列为 2025 年最受期待的 50 张专辑</a>。 NME 在其中写道：“自从 Central Cee 凭借 2022 年的《Doja》进入主流以来，由于与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave">Dave</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">Raye</a>等人的排行榜合作，Central Cee 无所不在。他并不是真正的新人，但他的首张录音室专辑《Can&#39;t Rush Greatness》仍然让人感觉像是一次盛大的到来。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/central-cee-and-21-savage-link-up-for-hard-hitting-new-collaboration-gbp-3829774">Central Cee 和 21 Savage 联手打造的新合作歌曲“GBP”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
泰勒·斯威夫特谈“令人心碎”的洛杉矶野火：“如此多的痛苦、损失和破坏” https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-on-heartwriting-los-angeles-wildfires-so-much-suffering-loss-and-destruction-3829762?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=泰勒-斯威夫特-令人心碎的洛杉矶野火-如此多的痛苦-损失-和破坏Surej SinghFri, 17 Jan 2025 03:53:35 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3829762 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她还分享了一份资源清单，敦促粉丝在有能力的情况下捐款</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-on-heartbreaking-los-angeles-wildfires-so-much-suffering-loss-and-destruction-3829762">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 发表关于“令人心碎”的洛杉矶山火的帖子：“如此多的痛苦、损失和破坏”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>谈到了毁灭性的洛杉矶野火——看看她下面是怎么说的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界告诉我们野火的“悲剧性”影响：“这种影响将持续多年”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周（1 月 7 日），洛杉矶<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">遭遇多场单独的野火</a>，摧毁了多个社区，并迫使超过 15 万居民撤离。大火已导致数千所房屋被烧毁，已造成<a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/live-updates/la-fires-southern-california-containment-efforts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">27 人死亡</a>、 <a href="https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2025-01-16/how-many-people-are-missing-from-the-los-angeles-fires" target="_blank" rel="noopener">31 人失踪</a>。</p><p>现在，斯威夫特<a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/taylorswift/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 Instagram Stories 上评论了加州的灾难</a>。她写道：“加利福尼亚州的大火摧毁了许多家庭，看到这些故事的发生令人心碎。如此多的痛苦、损失和破坏。当许多人开始经历人生中最具挑战性的时期时，也有许多令人惊叹的组织和团体联合起来帮助这些社区重建。” </p><figure id="attachment_3823675" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823675" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823675" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823675" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特。图片来源：Kevin Winter/TAS24/Getty Images for TAS Rights Management</figcaption></figure><p>她继续说道，她已经向多个组织捐款，并敦促追随者如果有能力也这样做：“这些是我捐赠过的组织。如果您觉得有必要或有能力捐款，请这样做。”</p><p>她重点介绍的组织和资源包括 211 LA、加州社区基金会、大洛杉矶仁人家园、洛杉矶消防局基金会、洛杉矶联合学区教育基金会和 MusiCares。</p><p>她捐款的组织之一直接救济组织感谢泰勒·斯威夫特“在支持那些受毁灭性野火影响的人们方面所表现出的令人难以置信的慷慨和同情心”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">感谢您<a href="https://twitter.com/taylorswift13?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@taylorswift13</a> ，感谢您为支持南加州毁灭性野火影响的人们提供的令人难以置信的慷慨和同情心。 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1faf6.png" alt="🫶" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/lafires?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#lafires</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Californiafires?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Californiafires</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/eaton?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#eaton</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/altadena?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#altadena</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/losangeles?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#losangeles</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/fires?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#fires</a> <a href="https://t.co/BKkGYUK3hY">pic.twitter.com/BKkGYUK3hY</a></p><p> - 直接救援 (@DirectRelief) <a href="https://twitter.com/DirectRelief/status/1880024402798211449?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025 年 1 月 16 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这并不是斯威夫特第一次为救援基金捐款，并召集粉丝在有能力和愿意的情况下提供支持。就在几个月前，她向 Feeding America <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-donates-5million-to-hurricane-helene-and-milton-relief-efforts-3801306">捐赠了高达 500 万美元，</a>用于飓风海伦和米尔顿的救援工作。</p><p>斯威夫特的山火救援捐款总额尚未公开。</p><p>斯威夫特并不是唯一一位在悲剧发生后帮助受影响社区的知名名人。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-foundation-announces-2-5million-donation-to-la-wildfire-relief-3828303">碧昂斯 (Beyoncé) 的 BeyGOOD 基金会已捐赠 250 万美元，</a>用于帮助洛杉矶山火的救灾工作。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">帕丽斯·希尔顿还为因火灾而流离失所的家庭发起了一项基金</a>，承诺捐款 10 万美元，并承诺匹配最多 10 万美元的捐款。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-spent-birthday-making-meals-for-families-hit-by-la-wildfires-3829226">戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl) 也在生日那天为受影响的家庭做饭</a>。</p><p>美国-墨西哥乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/american-mexican-fuerza-regida-rent-entire-hotel-shelter-victims-wildfires-3828174">Fuerza Regida 将整个酒店出租一​​周，为逃离山火的 50 个家庭提供庇护</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-wildfires-more-than-1000-music-professionals-supported-by-charity-musicares-3828869">洛杉矶野火：慈善机构支持超过 1000 名音乐专业人士 - 以下是寻求帮助的方法</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-urges-brands-gifting-her-clothing-to-instead-donate-it-to-those-affected-by-horrific-la-wildfires-3828185">Charli XCX 呼吁品牌赠送她的衣服“将它们送给真正需要它的人”。</a>随后，她分享了造型师 Lana Jay Lackey 组织的衣物捐赠活动的细节，并敦促其他人加入她的捐赠行列。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">阿丽亚娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>等人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">对野火造成的“令人心碎”的破坏做出了反应</a>，为需要帮助的人分享资源链接。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界的成员也向<em>《NME》</em>表示，他们受到了严重打击</a>，许多场馆、工作室和艺术家都受到了火灾的影响。</p><p>失去家园的人包括艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jhene-aiko-and-beyonces-mother-tina-knowles-reveal-theyve-lost-their-homes-in-the-la-wildfires-3827728">Jhené Aiko</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madlib-launches-fundraiser-to-help-him-and-his-family-rebuild-after-california-wildfires-3828493">Madlib</a> 、 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/share/BAUTM06tGW">Diane Warren</a> 、 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/share/BAivrNANDG">Harry Mack</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-guitarist-adrian-smiths-malibu-home-destroyed-in-wildfires-3828249">Iron Maiden 吉他手 Adrian Smith</a> 、加拿大摇滚乐队 Cola and Ought 的 Tim Darcy、流行二人组 Brijean、 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/share/_wJq_TYdD">30 Seconds To Mars 吉他手兼音乐总监 Stevie艾洛</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>的母亲<a href="https://www.instagram.com/share/BAGLulZeMf">蒂娜·诺尔斯</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-on-heartbreaking-los-angeles-wildfires-so-much-suffering-loss-and-destruction-3829762">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 发表关于“令人心碎”的洛杉矶山火的帖子：“如此多的痛苦、损失和破坏”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
